This paper deals with optimizing caching in cellular networks, which is a topic related to network optimization and information theory. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization problems, which could place it in cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper uses analytical solutions and heuristics, which could place it in cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
